    <h3>What are Flashcards?</h3>
    <p>Flashcads are cards with a question in the front and an answer in the back.
    You can create your own Flashcards or use the ones which have been created by other students.
    The Flashcards you choose are added to your stack of cards.
    The goal is to know and memorize the content of the cards that are relevant to you.</p>
